---
title: Tofu Massaman Curry with Green Beans and Zesty Rice
description: This Tofu Massaman Curry is bursting full of flavours and make the perfect dinner night option, from HelloFresh. Cook up a fresh start!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tofu-massaman-curry-1feb6117-3637d807.jpg
